are deodorants and hair care products it operates in the americas europe the middle east and africa emea and asia pacific receive news  ratings for elizabeth arden inc daily  enter your email address below to receive a concise daily summary of the latest news and analysts ratings for elizabeth arden inc and related companies with marketbeatcoms free daily email newsletter latest news leave a reply click here to cancel reply name required mail will not be published required website newsmedia  sears holdings corporation close search bar search mobile navigation sears holdings corporation newsmedia press releases jul  sears launches kenmore products on amazoncom including alexaenabled smart appliances jul  the kmart® summer blowout is here to help you soak up summer jul  sears holdings announces secured line of credit facility and real estate transactions jun  sears opens first appliances  mattresses store in pharr texas jun  sears holdings provides strategic restructuring update press kits sears press kits kmart press kits look books sears kmart press releases sears holdings sears roebuck and co kmart subscribe rss feed search shc speaks media inquiries company statements press kits sears kmart media gallery images lookbooks videos  sears brands llc press releases  sears holdings corporation close search bar search mobile navigation sears holdings corporation press releases archives                                     category all sears holdings kmart sears roebuck and co jul  sears launches kenmore products on amazoncom including alexaenabled smart appliances jul  the kmart® summer blowout is here to help you soak up summer jul  sears holdings announces secured line of credit facility and real estate transactions jun  sears opens first appliances  mattresses store in pharr texas jun  sears holdings provides strategic restructuring update jun  beat the summer heat with new smart room air conditioners from the kenmore® brand jun  regatta great outdoors makes american d